    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >要么拥抱内心的恶魔，要么被它吞噬。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598780/extras/5fa52114c80cb011fd6cdd41848df360.poster.avif?t=1764856166\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598780/extras/5fa52114c80cb011fd6cdd41848df360.webm?t=1764856166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598780/extras/5fa52114c80cb011fd6cdd41848df360.mp4?t=1764856166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >厄运缠身的 Polly 逃离了噩梦般的孤儿院…却发现自己被困在了地下世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这座城市被迷雾笼罩。那是一种致命的迷雾。据说，一旦看到这样的景象，就得万分小心。当致命迷雾逼近时，你的迷雾手环就会发出红光示警。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598780/extras/0d493f3de38574e484d1993dc4e2523b.poster.avif?t=1764856166\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598780/extras/0d493f3de38574e484d1993dc4e2523b.webm?t=1764856166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598780/extras/0d493f3de38574e484d1993dc4e2523b.mp4?t=1764856166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会在异世界遇到各种居民。并非所有居民都会与你为敌，但也没有谁会与你为伍。无论事态如何发展，永远不要忘记让你坠入这个深渊的誓言与契约。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598780/extras/6e0a610f51c0095b6b75343ccc63a419.poster.avif?t=1764856166\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598780/extras/6e0a610f51c0095b6b75343ccc63a419.webm?t=1764856166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598780/extras/6e0a610f51c0095b6b75343ccc63a419.mp4?t=1764856166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好迎接独特的游戏体验吧。本游戏融合了世界探索以及横向和俯视视角的战斗。古老的禁忌知识将增强你的力量。每掌握一个新的法术，Polly 的力量就会变得更加致命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598780/extras/562caa3ec26cfe98e658cb99e7d07617.poster.avif?t=1764856166\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598780/extras/562caa3ec26cfe98e658cb99e7d07617.webm?t=1764856166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598780/extras/562caa3ec26cfe98e658cb99e7d07617.mp4?t=1764856166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索诡异之地，直面 Polly 记忆中挥之不去的恐怖身影，掌握禁忌法术，为了自由而战。你会成功逃脱，还是会先被恶魔吞噬呢？</p>",
